---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Base title="tama96 — virtual pet for your desktop">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-split">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h1>tama96</h1>
        <p>A virtual pet for your desktop, terminal, or AI agent. Inspired by the 1996 original. Your care choices shape who your pet becomes.</p>
        <div class="cta">
          <a href="/download" class="btn-primary">Download</a>
          <a href="/docs" class="btn-secondary">Documentation</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-img">
        <img src="/tama96-desktop.png" alt="tama96 desktop app" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grid">
    <article>
      <h3>Desktop app</h3>
      <p>Pixel LCD display with clickable icons. System tray, background ticks, desktop notifications. Always-on-top so your pet stays visible.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h3>Terminal</h3>
      <p>Braille pixel sprites rendered in your terminal. Runs standalone or connects to the desktop app as a client. Single binary, zero dependencies.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h3>AI agent</h3>
      <p>Bundled MCP server lets AI tools feed, play with, and care for your pet. Per-action permissions and rate limits keep things under control.</p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="showcase">
    <div class="showcase-secondary">
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/tama96-tui.png" alt="tama96 terminal TUI" />
        <span class="img-label">Terminal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/tama96-mcp-tools.png" alt="tama96 MCP tools" />
        <span class="img-label">MCP agent</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="evo">
    <h2>Evolution</h2>
    <p>Real-time lifecycle. One day equals one pet year. Hunger and happiness decay, poop accumulates, sickness sets in. How you respond determines which of 11 characters your pet becomes.</p>
    <div class="chain">Egg → Baby → Child → Teen → Adult</div>
    <p class="small">Best care leads to Mametchi. Neglect leads to Tarakotchi. <a href="/docs">Full evolution chart in the docs.</a></p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero {
      padding: 48px 0 56px;
    }
    .hero-split {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .hero-text { flex: 1; }
    .hero-text h1 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .hero-text p {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .hero-img {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 240px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-img img { width: 100%; display: block; }
    .cta { display: flex; gap: 12px; }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      background: var(--text);
      color: var(--bg);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: opacity 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.8; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      transition: all 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: #999; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 64px;
    }
    .grid article {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: 28px;
    }
    .grid h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .grid p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .screenshot {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .showcase { margin-bottom: 64px; }
    .showcase-secondary {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .showcase-img {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #1e1e1e;
      position: relative;
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    }
    .showcase-img img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: block;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: top left;
    }
    .img-label {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 10px;
      left: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #ccc;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .showcase-secondary { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    .evo {
      padding-top: 32px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .evo h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .evo p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .chain {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .small { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-tertiary); }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero-split { flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
      .hero-img { width: 200px; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-text h1 { font-size: 32px; }
      .showcase-secondary { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</Base>
